    <ArticleWrap>

<h1>Best AI Tools for Students 2026</h1>
<p><em>Last updated: June 27, 2026</em></p>

<p>Artificial intelligence is transforming how students learn, write, research, and study. In 2026, a new generation of AI tools makes it easier than ever to draft essays, debug code, summarize lectures, build presentations, and prepare for exams — often for free. We tested dozens of AI tools across every category that matters to students, from writing assistants and research copilots to coding tutors and presentation designers. Here are our top picks to help you boost your grades without breaking the bank.</p>

