<tr><td>✔ Generous free tier for students</td><td>✘ May produce overly verbose responses</td></tr>
<tr><td>✔ Excellent natural language understanding</td><td>✘ No built-in plagiarism checker</td></tr>
<tr><td>✔ Code interpreter for data analysis</td><td>✘ Internet search requires manual activation</td></tr>
</tbody>
